dataStructure.name: sid.org.tmforum.tip.product.prod.ProductBundle
dataStructure.description:
A ProductBundle is an instantiation of BundledProductOffering which keeps the business terms under which the customer purchased the product bundle (using a BundledProductOffering).

This entity is optional
